name: 'Forward!': 2013/ 2nd Panel - Giclée Mini Print
description:
'Forward' 

2013

2nd Panel

Presenting the 1st Panel limited edition mini print of the artist's 2013 painting 'Forward'. Comprised of real subjects painted from London's South Bank over 3 month period. Forward looks at the collective direction of humanity, whilst it is also a celebration of multicultural roots.  

Signed, numbered and dated.

Limited to a run of 11

Certificate of authenticity included 

Printed on high quality museum standard German Etching paper 350gm


Size:

100cm (L) x 46cm (H)

(2/3rd's size of the original painting)


Delivery: 

Mailed unframed and sent rolled in secure cardboard tube mailer via a reliable tracked service. 

Depending on the location, please allow a 7 to 12 days to process and receive the order.



Thank you
